{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somehow, our transport was taken to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never knew the reason why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only thing that I could think of, that they needed labor, because we immediately were put to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I will explain you what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After debarkation in-- in-- in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Buchenwald, after we unloaded all the dead ones, there were maybe 20% that didn't make it, possibly more.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What they did, they brought us into camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a cold, winter night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was November.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very cold in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the first thing they did, they undressed us They took every possession what we had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't have anything, papers, a picture, a keys, or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they took everything away from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And for hours they let us stand in the nude.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There is nothing as demoralizing and dehumanizing as standing cold in the nude, men and women together, and not knowing what next, when the door will open up, what next will be.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Finally, after several hours, people were falling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were freezing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] They took us to a room where they had a huge tub, a gigantic tub, which had a solution in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Probably, I believe, it was DDT dissolvant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there were two Germans standing on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And one by one we had to go through that tub, dunk into the tub.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Kept us down for about a second or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then wet, get out again, and wait.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Many, many people just drowned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They just wanted to drown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They didn't want to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was-- that was de-licing or whatever they believed in.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
